eb7923f2ae40c2df8cca512fdb9e3b4c679c8b75","tid":342831,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T11:11:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果同佢講個攝影師 一個係90後 一個係80後 一個係60後呢</blockquote><br />\n一定老屈90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}